SAFA Nelson Mandelabaai skop die hervatting van die Derde Liga sommer vuurwarm af. Die naweek word daar ’n double header van games aangebied. Die Madibaz het nie die tweede helfte van die seisoen goed begin nie nadat PE Sundowns hulle Vrydag 1-0 geklop het. Die uitslag los die Madibaz in gevaar om agter te raak by die topspanne as hulle nie vinnig die oorwinnings inryg nie. Met Vrydag se sege is Sundowns nou die topspan met 16 liga­punte ná ag wedstryde. Major Chiefs, Camper United en Bay Tigers is ook tans op 16 punte. Major Chiefs is egter die enigste span wat sover nog onoorwonne is in die liga. Die Madibaz het wel ’n wedstryd minder as dié spanne gespeel. As die Madibaz dus die naweek albei hulle wedstryde wen, kan hulle weer onder die topspanne eindig. Derde Liga-uitslae: Motherwell Academy 0, Bay Tigers 2; Lion City 1, Roaring Tigers 3; Camper United 2, Young Teenagers 0; Highland Spurs 3, School of Excellence 2; Golden Aces 1, Stinging Bees 1; Despatch Pioneers 3, Westville Academy 2. Derde Liga-bepalings: VRYDAG: Madibaz t Bay Tigers FC – 2nd Avenue – 19:00 SATERDAG: New Brighton Academy t Lion City – CHEVROLET – 9:30; School of Excellence FC t Despatch Pioneers – NU2 – 11:00; Stinging Bees t Camper United – CHEVROLET – 11:30; Motherwell Academy t Madibaz – NU2 – 13:00; PE Sundowns t Highland Spurs FC – CHEVROLET – 13:30; Bay Tigers FC t Major Chiefs – ZWIDE – 15:00; Westville Academy FC t Young Teenagers – THEMBANI – 15:00; Roaring Tigers t Golden Aces – CHEVROLET – 15:30. SONDAG: Camper United t Roaring Tigers – NU2 – 13:00; Westville Academy FC t Stinging Bees – THEMBANI – 13:00; Lion City t Major Chiefs – NU2 – 15:00; Highland Spurs FC t Motherwell Academy – JABAVU – 15:00; Golden Aces t New Brighton Academy – ZWIDE – 15:00; Despatch Pioneers t PE Sundowns – KAYAMANDI – 15:00; Young Teenagers t School of Excellence FC – PLEK NOG ONBEKEND – 15:00.